---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 548
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=Man Created for Contemplation
By: Eckhart
---
The creature pleasures of the soul God has no stomach for, and when
she realizes this she discards the joys in which God has no share. ...
For God is spirit and he en-spirits the soul who, in her spiritual
nature, belongs to an order above creatures.
